! Components Facade Showcase

This tiddler demonstrates the facade layer for the components plugin. Facades expose a simple parameter + slot API, hiding the internal mixin machinery.

!! 1. Standalone Pills (minimal)

Multi-select pills with default styling — just pass `elements` and go:

<$transclude $tiddler="$:/plugins/rimir/components/pills"
	elements="alpha beta gamma delta epsilon"
	selection="multi"
	state="$:/state/showcase/pills-basic"/>

!! 2. Single-Select Pills

Only one pill can be active at a time:

<$transclude $tiddler="$:/plugins/rimir/components/pills"
	elements="red green blue yellow"
	selection="single"
	state="$:/state/showcase/pills-single"/>

!! 3. Pills with Filtering + Custom View + on-select

Filter popup, custom rendering via `view` slot, and `on-select` action logging:

<$transclude $tiddler="$:/plugins/rimir/components/pills"
	elements="p-1 p-2 p-3 p-4 p-5 p-6 p-7 p-8"
	filterable="yes"
	selection="multi"
	state="$:/state/showcase/pills-filtered">
	<$fill $name="view">
		''<$text text={{{[<element>uppercase[]]}}}/>''
	</$fill>
	<$fill $name="on-select">
		<$action-log message=`Pill selected: $(element)$ (modifier: $(modifier)$)`/>
	</$fill>
</$transclude>

!! 4. Vertical Tabs with Nested Pills

Demonstrates vtabs with sections, actions, links, and nested pill subcomponents.

* ''sec'' (sections): click to expand/collapse child elements
* ''act'' (actions): clicking stores the last-clicked action in state — shown below the component
* ''lnk'' (links): clicking navigates to the element as a tiddler title
* ''sco'' (subcomponents): nested pills with independent selection state — no `$unset` needed because `$fill` content runs in the caller's scope

<$transclude $tiddler="$:/plugins/rimir/components/vtabs"
	elements="section-1 act-11 act-12 lnk-11 scomp-11 scomp-12"
	type-fn="[<element>prefix[section-]then[sec]]~[<element>prefix[act-]then[act]]~[<element>prefix[lnk-]then[lnk]]~[<element>prefix[scomp-]then[sco]]"
	state="$:/state/showcase/vtabs">

	<$fill $name="view-sec">
		<strong><$text text={{{[<element>removeprefix[section-]addprefix[Section ]]}}}/></strong>
	</$fill>

	<$fill $name="view-act">
		&#9654; Action: <<element>>
	</$fill>

	<$fill $name="view-lnk">
		&#128279; <<element>>
	</$fill>

	<$fill $name="view-sco">
		<$transclude $tiddler="$:/plugins/rimir/components/pills"
			elements={{{[<element>match[scomp-11]then[p-1 p-2 p-3 p-4]else[x-1 x-2 x-3 x-4]]}}}
			selection="multi"
			state=`$:/state/showcase/vtabs:$(element)$`/>
	</$fill>
</$transclude>

Last action clicked: ''<$text text={{$:/state/showcase/vtabs:last-click}}/>''
